        <item>
          <title>Apple Introduces Swiftly 1.0: A Version Manager for the Swift Programming Language</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Swiftly 1.0 is a version manager for Swift that makes it easier to install, manage, and update the Swift tool chain. Apple has officially supported it as part of the core Swift tool chain.]]></description>
